#: model:ir.model,name:theme_orchid.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "主题用途"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Tony Fred, Floral Director"
msgstr "Tony Fred，花艺总监"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Tony leads the creative vision for the shop."
msgstr "Tony 是这家商店的创意总监。"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Vibrant hues of orange and red capture the warmth and beauty of a summer "
"evening."
msgstr "鲜艳的橙色和红色捕捉到了夏夜的温暖和美丽。"
